            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.2.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 3.2.0</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>Smarter file names for more document and media types</li><li>Templates now focus on renaming first, with Finder tags and Spotlight metadata off by default</li><li>Renaming can skip unused metadata work when tags or Spotlight metadata are disabled</li><li>More reliable free-tier limit handling and quieter recoverable warnings</li></ul>
]]></description>
